gems.name: google-cloud-cloud_quotas-v1
gems.info: Cloud Quotas API provides Google Cloud service consumers with management and observability for resource usage, quotas, and restrictions of the services they consume. Note that google-cloud-cloud_quotas-v1 is a version-specific client library. For most uses, we recommend installing the main client library google-cloud-cloud_quotas instead. See the readme for more details.
